    "en": {
      "title": "3,000 buses are not running today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been reported that the number of private bus services has reduced in all provinces today due to fuel shortage.",
        "To this end, Sarath Vijithakumara, President of All Provinces Private Bus Owners Association, has said that about 3000 buses have suspended their daily transport services today.",
        "He said that while there are 3200 private buses in all the provinces under the control of the National Transport Council, only 200 buses are in service today."
      ],
